@startuml
title Mini GFS - Sequence Diagram

actor Client
participant Master
participant ChunkServer1 as CS1
participant ChunkServer2 as CS2

== Node Registration ==
CS1 -> Master: POST /register (addr=CS1)
Master --> CS1: OK

CS2 -> Master: POST /register (addr=CS2)
Master --> CS2: OK

== Heartbeat ==
loop every 5s
    CS1 -> Master: POST /heartbeat
    CS2 -> Master: POST /heartbeat
end

== File Upload ==
Client -> Master: Upload Request (file.txt, size)

Master -> Master: Split into chunks
Master -> Master: Select nodes for each chunk

Master --> Client: Chunk locations\n(chunk1->CS1, chunk2->CS2)

Client -> CS1: PUT /chunk1 (data)
CS1 --> Client: OK

Client -> CS2: PUT /chunk2 (data)
CS2 --> Client: OK

== File Download ==
Client -> Master: GET file.txt metadata

Master --> Client: Chunk locations

Client -> CS1: GET /chunk1
CS1 --> Client: chunk1 data

Client -> CS2: GET /chunk2
CS2 --> Client: chunk2 data

Client -> Client: Merge chunks

@enduml
